				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \mathit{GRD} = \mathit{FWHM}_{\mathit{LSF}} \cdot d. $$\end{document} A common performance metric used to describe commercial remote sensing systems is the optical quality factor (Q): 10Q=FWHMLSF⋅fp,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
